{"data": {"node": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "4038407439503919", "organization": {"id": "608197834364884", "viewer_permissions": [], "application_groupings": {"nodes": [{"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "4038407439503919"}]}, "id": "172103444351718"}, {"viewer_has_update_access": false, "full_applications": {"nodes": [{"id": "8714253315313680"}]}, "id": "736023364813844"}]}}, "firstRevision": {"nodes": [{"application": {"id": "4038407439503919", "release_date": 1623457066, "is_concept": false, "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "scheduled_offers": {"count": 12}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "7544239385587356"}, "id": "4182904848389764"}]}}, "binary": null, "live_binary": null, "created_date": 1729584275, "id": "8986719204672693", "is_initial_release": false, "name_with_fallback": "v20", "pdp_metadata_with_fallback": {"version": 19, "application": {"is_concept": false, "latest_released_pdp_metadata": {"id": "8440204589324160"}, "release_status": "RELEASED", "id": "4038407439503919"}, "id": "8440204589324160", "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED"}, "release_date": null, "administration_status": "APPROVED", "is_first": false, "release_status": "PENDING", "release_type": "SCHEDULED", "pdp_metadata": null, "review_messages": ["", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031479_1026147248395845_3494489515268466820_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=pFJQ-dpjArAQ7kNvgHut3-j&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCDvW865EuZuUrbq-7eq4EHFiSDfzhtrb0T35wEsn76HQ&oe=674063CB"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "JUST HOOPS", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_category": {"context_category": "GAMES", "id": "2743326035925534"}, "context_topics": [{"topic_name": "Sports", "id": "2776542286000603"}, {"topic_name": "Arcade", "id": "1592192974313489"}], "release_date": 1623457066, "lastRevision": {"nodes": [{"id": "454688815665387", "release_type": "SCHEDULED", "administration_status": "APPROVED", "pdp_metadata": {"application": {"default_locale": "en_US", "id": "4038407439503919", "is_first_party": false, "enables_in_app_ads": false, "is_concept": false, "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF"}, "iarc_cert": {"id": "1093074057843753"}, "iarc_email": null, "msrp": null, "translations": {"nodes": [{"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "894075081437802", "locale": "es_ES", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "In da Hoop!", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Ahora y por primera vez en la historia, te ofrecemos un videojuego de b\u00e1squetbol al que puedes jugar a mano limpia. \n\nIn da Hoop! es un juego \u00fanico que te devuelve el ambiente de los a\u00f1os 80 y el encanto del b\u00e1squetbol de sal\u00f3n. \n\nEl juego propone toda una serie de modos para que tanto adultos como ni\u00f1os puedan divertirse y mantenerse activos. Puedes elegir entre relajarte y jugar de forma informal o ser competitivo.\n\nEn su primera versi\u00f3n, el juego te ofrece un modo Entrenamiento, que incluye los niveles Tutorial, Terminal de arcade y Cesta de b\u00e1squetbol. Tambi\u00e9n puedes competir en modo Juego directo y tratar de superar las mejores puntuaciones en l\u00ednea. \n\nDespu\u00e9s de su lanzamiento, se a\u00f1adir\u00e1n nuevos contenidos con sus correspondientes actualizaciones. \u00a1En breve podr\u00e1s jugar online con otros jugadores! Tambi\u00e9n se agregar\u00e1n nuevos modos y skins. \n\nEs un nuevo producto de los desarrolladores de los exitosos juegos de Ubisoft como Just Dance y Rabbids. \n", "short_description": "Ahora y por primera vez en la historia, te ofrecemos un videojuego de b\u00e1squetbol al que puedes jugar a mano limpia. \n\nIn da Hoop! es un juego \u00fanico que te devuelve el ambiente de los a\u00f1os 80 y el encanto del b\u00e1squetbol de sal\u00f3n. \n\nEl juego propone toda una serie de modos para que tanto adultos como ni\u00f1os puedan divertirse y mantenerse activos. Puedes elegir entre relajarte y jugar de forma informal o ser competitivo."}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "736858776974972", "locale": "fr_FR", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "In da Hoop!", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Pour la premi\u00e8re fois dans l'histoire, jouez \u00e0 un jeu vid\u00e9o de basketball \u00e0 mains nues ! \n\nIn da Hoop ! est une exp\u00e9rience VR unique qui vous fait ressentir le plaisir du basket dans votre salon. \n\nDans une ambiance de salle d'arcade des ann\u00e9es 80, le jeu propose une vari\u00e9t\u00e9 de modes funs et stimulants pour divertir tous les membres de la famille. Jouez en mode tranquille ou essayez de battre les meilleurs scores du classement mondial !\n\nLe jeu vous donne d'abord acc\u00e8s au mode entra\u00eenement, qui comprend le tutoriel, avant d'aller aux niveaux plus avanc\u00e9s de la borne d'arcade et du panier de Basket. Lorsque vous vous sentez pr\u00eat pour la comp\u00e9tition, entrez dans le mode 'Partie rapide' et battez les meilleurs joueurs en ligne ! \n\nLes prochaines mises \u00e0 jour int\u00e9grerons de nouveaux contenus, notamment un mode en ligne pour jouer en direct avec d'autres joueurs.\nGardez un \u0153il sur les nouveaux modes et skins ajout\u00e9s en permanence !\n", "short_description": "Pour la premi\u00e8re fois dans l'histoire, jouez \u00e0 un jeu vid\u00e9o de basketball \u00e0 mains nues ! \n\nIn da Hoop ! est une exp\u00e9rience VR unique qui vous fait ressentir le plaisir du basket dans votre salon. \n\nDans une ambiance de salle d'arcade des ann\u00e9es 80, le jeu propose une vari\u00e9t\u00e9 de modes funs et stimulants pour divertir tous les membres de la famille. Jouez en mode tranquille ou essayez de battre les meilleurs scores du classement mondial !"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "hero3.png", "id": "1211520005945854", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75422381_1211520009279187_518651254030611021_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=B05hWZUkyhwQ7kNvgHGhX50&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCTQGauabincnG-SyvVou7sRWWLKFWPeJv8PQnFBVMm5g&oe=67407E1D"}, {"file_name": "mini landscape 2.png", "id": "304857601341333", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001669_304857604674666_7389359364480074074_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=p5JPVwaUu_YQ7kNvgHCjafo&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD0_CP2HzCA3OoQc42BKMy8_1u8R1HaO-o1e53Ww2EPxQ&oe=67405E8A"}, {"file_name": "mocup_stor_portrait.png", "id": "3787263714685548", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982604_3787263718018881_797958239632390981_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=hsOjMyL6PqwQ7kNvgGfJkT5&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBxNd3GcjBF_PZ4feJLG_pKwIOawd91wdfLvkn_TB8RjQ&oe=6740720A"}, {"file_name": "square.png", "id": "449081116179281", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982526_449081119512614_3768578882476773182_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=OoZjmLftEBYQ7kNvgEUpxES&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBaqpmHQaj-u9VvBAiSu4qdH8F66140EgBbEVgNUDDK7Q&oe=674084FC"}, {"file_name": "landscape.png", "id": "312667700206094", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035469_312667703539427_7235711557268766364_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=O3zQRUHPZKIQ7kNvgEdaCko&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDnXjRSDgFyizM9EqtIhU2IWeb-B0HazV2h_VikOhPvOg&oe=67406E5B"}, {"file_name": "Logo-InDaHoop_reduit 512 512.png", "id": "135667688446874", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031424_135667695113540_694440480643248802_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=eApkuNts91MQ7kNvgEOJQWl&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBsxqJSNIQc_TDj9Ubvcg01PXZ1QnMfx60xwWnzxRC3HA&oe=67407BD7"}, {"file_name": "Logo-InDaHoop_grand_format.png", "id": "512855063456568", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035330_512855066789901_6980918997351528256_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ee50bhet0OEQ7kNvgHPSOOr&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBPP5bSRTsqw4OjQI5nWrbb9CeHzCZqN3u1Pv7ZGTmFhw&oe=6740885E"}]}, "id": "548670876057986", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "CabinetShot.png", "id": "477574000334858", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75280981_477574007001524_5463638564135400124_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=92X6X1d3ngoQ7kNvgHcSnCx&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD_Xc22DOR8D3JhPUvjbJvGpomTblSxeAWh6lEkrJbU1g&oe=674064FD"}, {"file_name": "WadloShot.png", "id": "417254609364181", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75485578_417254612697514_8913667014127081770_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=7JboqiiI5OAQ7kNvgEVYSRy&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDKcTA3_U-rCXvFbHsJc4HJuptfNSM5DY2x5E7qY_xOJQ&oe=67407ABB"}, {"file_name": "Menus.png", "id": "206757967667242", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75356791_206757971000575_6368155350379327517_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_aid=0&_nc_ohc=yihP287j86MQ7kNvgGlm8Vy&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCY5ymvRBrp41dOlmWNe_Wuw1XwymIBP73hGHOgpZttcQ&oe=67407221"}, {"file_name": "PlayerStats.png", "id": "252809909913532", "uri": "https://scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974901_252809913246865_4799631131884614163_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=T2GRAk7oGQ0Q7kNvgG3GRa_&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAO75BRCdCHjl79ZIDyMFI4U8wPI8bBjAenU0dDY_EQ5A&oe=67406780"}, {"file_name": "Room.png", "id": "243900480810191", "uri": "https://scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75630195_243900484143524_7582605456043229273_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=r0el-RBMKyoQ7kNvgEKYepB&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-ams4-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCrSvvj9asCRCmekSDrPmu25ItY6KlY7L-IIQ8LIlu60A&oe=67407D01"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "In da Hoop!", "keywords": [], "long_description": "For the first time in history, you can play a basketball video game with just your bare hands! \n\nIn da Hoop! is a unique VR experience that captures the satisfying thrill of basketball in your living room. \n\nSporting a fun 80's arcade vibe, the game comes with a variety of fun and challenging modes to keep every member of the family entertained.\nPlay in a relaxed casual mode to challenge yourself or take on the global leaderboard and try to beat the high scores!  It\u2019s up to you but it\u2019s fun for all!\n\nThe game starts you off with access to the Training mode, includes the Tutorial, before letting you into the more advanced Arcade and Basketball levels. When you feel ready for some competition, enter into Quick Play mode and try to beat the high scores online! \n\nFuture updates will be filled with new content including an Online mode to play live with other players. Keep an eye out for new modes and skins added continuously!\n", "short_description": "For the first time in history, you can play a basketball video game with just your bare hands!\n\nIn da Hoop! is a unique VR experience that captures the satisfying thrill of basketball in your living room. Sporting a fun 80's arcade vibe, the game comes with a variety of fun and challenging modes to keep every member of the family entertained.\nPlay in a relaxed casual mode to challenge yourself or take on the global leaderboard and try to beat the high scores! It\u2019s up to you but it\u2019s fun for all!"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "268362378288005", "locale": "es_LA", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "In da Hoop!", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Ahora y por primera vez en la historia, te ofrecemos un videojuego de b\u00e1squetbol al que puedes jugar a mano limpia. \n\nIn da Hoop! es un juego \u00fanico que te devuelve el ambiente de los a\u00f1os 80 y el encanto del b\u00e1squetbol de sal\u00f3n. \n\nEl juego propone toda una serie de modos para que tanto adultos como ni\u00f1os puedan divertirse y mantenerse activos. Puedes elegir entre relajarte y jugar de forma informal o ser competitivo.\n\nEn su primera versi\u00f3n, el juego te ofrece un modo Entrenamiento, que incluye los niveles Tutorial, Terminal de arcade y Cesta de b\u00e1squetbol. Tambi\u00e9n puedes competir en modo Juego directo y tratar de superar las mejores puntuaciones en l\u00ednea. \n\nDespu\u00e9s de su lanzamiento, se a\u00f1adir\u00e1n nuevos contenidos con sus correspondientes actualizaciones. \u00a1En breve podr\u00e1s jugar online con otros jugadores! Tambi\u00e9n se agregar\u00e1n nuevos modos y skins. \n\nEs un nuevo producto de los desarrolladores de los exitosos juegos de Ubisoft como Just Dance y Rabbids. \n", "short_description": "Ahora y por primera vez en la historia, te ofrecemos un videojuego de b\u00e1squetbol al que puedes jugar a mano limpia. \n\nIn da Hoop! es un juego \u00fanico que te devuelve el ambiente de los a\u00f1os 80 y el encanto del b\u00e1squetbol de sal\u00f3n. \n\nEl juego propone toda una serie de modos para que tanto adultos como ni\u00f1os puedan divertirse y mantenerse activos. Puedes elegir entre relajarte y jugar de forma informal o ser competitivo.\n"}]}, "dev